w }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[3861,1420],"id":"51fcaef8-784e-49d5-9465-9ffdba781451","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### When Chat Message Received\n\nOpens a hosted chat session; every user message starts an execution with `chatInput` + `sessionId`.\n\nNext: Keep Valid Requests","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"b4de85cc-b8a9-b3e5-0a73-6416b323e3f3","name":"Note: When Chat Message Received"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Keep Valid Requests\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Classify with AI","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"a6b6dc11-c38a-ef9a-cdc5-8b8e76c3db85","name":"Note: Keep Valid Requests"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Classify with AI\n\nLLM classification into: Question, Complaint, Feedback (+fallback). Output port order matches this list.\n\nPorts: ①→ Store as Question · ②→ Store as Complaint, Capture Failure Context · ③→ Store as Feedback · ④→ Alert Slack — Other\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"7fe1168f-dd0e-400d-bf71-62dc01c76430","name":"Note: Classify with AI"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenRouter Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Classify with AI** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenRouter API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[561,1090],"id":"26f22416-1516-0718-bda0-b4372064b0b1","name":"Note: OpenRouter Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Question\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,40],"id":"0448c8d7-449e-de37-7cec-51cedb7f9103","name":"Note: Store as Question"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Complaint\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,490],"id":"bc0dadab-0c72-458c-345a-6dcf2569872f","name":"Note: Store as Complaint"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Feedback\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,940],"id":"849b5529-7daf-31b8-dd94-c112cd25c025","name":"Note: Store as Feedback"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Alert Slack — Other\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,1390],"id":"7439f187-9b63-70ae-1833-dc9fda8d8614","name":"Note: Alert Slack — Other"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Reunite Branches\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty query","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2505,520],"id":"a47ff990-4a4f-d8ff-32d3-d81b0e440757","name":"Note: Reunite Branches"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty query\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,520],"id":"7af27067-7ea2-319a-275c-72ec4cff88e4","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty query"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Send Summary to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"07d65e29-948d-70be-150a-9d2593ca1270","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"9ce44f67-93c1-ea9a-1486-6694b815fd97","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,1540],"id":"a7fff7b7-fac3-0091-8f16-d197bb071954","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,1540],"id":"c84ae892-bf80-3315-8b99-89344a6ec835","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Reply to user questions without manual work for Task Automation\n\n**Pattern:** Chatbot Responder · **Level:** Core · **Trigger:** Chat\n\n## What it does\nReply to user questions without manual work for Task Automation. It responds live to chat messages.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual task automation is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWhen Chat Message Received → Keep Valid Requests → Classify with AI → Store as Question → Reunite Branches → Guard Non-Empty query → Tag Pipeline Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to chatbot responder without manual effort\n- Anyone automating task automation in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; OpenRouter API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"75d5d084-c0b5-1057-11a6-6c24e8ec0d01","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"c154d42d-6edc-a941-1a50-695a05b2f47c","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"fcb04655-0191-be04-ce02-24083ba657c0","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your task automation process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"9dcec901-c64e-fd4b-0835-2ca92fada681","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"When Chat Message Received":{"main":[[{"node":"Keep Valid Requests","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Keep Valid Requests":{"main":[[{"node":"Classify with AI","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenRouter Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Classify with AI","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Classify with AI":{"main":[[{"node":"Store as Question","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Store as Complaint","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Store as Feedback","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Alert Slack — Other","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Question":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Complaint":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Feedback":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Alert Slack — Other":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Reunite Branches":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty query","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty query":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"b507ba0a-64d9-496f-bd46-67204d078250","id":"FDX01328"}